OL,3,CCocaine-fuelled driver jailed for
OL,4,Ckilling teenager as he waited at bus
OL,5,Cstop
OL,7,FA cocaine-fuelled driver who caused
OL,8,Fthe death of a teenager as he waited
OL,9,Fat a bus stop with his girlfriend has
OL,10,Fbeen jailed for seven years and eight
OL,11,Fmonths.
OL,13,FSteven Wallace was five times the drug-
OL,14,Fdrive limit when he got behind the
OL,15,Fwheel of his BMW 320i in Newcastle
OL,16,Fearlier this year and careered into 19-
OL,17,Fyear-old Joe Scott and his girlfriend.
OL,19,FToday Joe's family said the sentence
OL,20,FWallace received is "an absolute joke"
OL,21,Fand criticised the justice system.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
