OL,3,CCocaine-fuelled driver jailed for
OL,4,Ckilling teenager as he waited at bus
OL,5,Cstop
OL,7,FHis aunt, Clare Armstrong, said: "He
OL,8,Fgot seven years and eight months,
OL,9,Fwhich is nothing. He'll serve two
OL,10,Fthirds of that. The whole system needs
OL,11,Frevamped.
OL,13,F"What's seven years compared to the
OL,14,Flife that he has taken? He's not only
OL,15,Ftaken Joe's life but he's taken the
OL,16,Ffamily's life."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
