OL,7,FDuring the incident on 15 October last
OL,8,Fyear, Joe's last act was to pull his
OL,9,Fgirlfriend out of the way of the car,
OL,10,Fsaving her life. His dad said this
OL,11,Ffinal act made him a "real hero".
OL,13,FHis girlfriend suffered serious
OL,14,Finjuries.
OL,16,FMs Armstrong also paid tribute to her
OL,17,Fson outside of Newcastle Crown Court.
OL,18,FShe said: "He was the loveliest lad
OL,19,Fyou'd ever meet. He had his whole life
OL,20,Fahead of him.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
