OL,3,CCocaine-fuelled driver jailed for
OL,4,Ckilling teenager as he waited at bus
OL,5,Cstop
OL,7,F"His life was snatched away by a dirty
OL,8,Flittle coward who thought it was
OL,9,Falright to get high as a kite on
OL,10,Fcocaine, drive a car, drive nearly
OL,11,Ftwice the speed limit."
OL,13,FWallace, of Lonnen Avenue, Newcastle,
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to causing death and
OL,15,Fserious injury by dangerous driving,
OL,16,Fdrug driving, failing to stop after an
OL,17,Faccident and driving without insurance
OL,18,Fat Newcastle Crown Court on Monday 15
OL,19,FJuly.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
