OL,3,CCocaine-fuelled driver jailed for
OL,4,Ckilling teenager as he waited at bus
OL,5,Cstop
OL,7,FHe was sentenced to seven years and
OL,8,Feight months on Friday 11 October.
OL,10,FFollowing the hearing, Sergeant Craig
OL,11,FBartle, of Northumbria Police, said:
OL,12,F"First and foremost, we would like to
OL,13,Fpay tribute to Joe's family and loved
OL,14,Fones.
OL,16,F"The last year has understandably been
OL,17,Fincredibly difficult for them and we
OL,18,Fwill continue to support them in any
OL,19,Fway we can.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
