OL,3,CCocaine-fuelled driver jailed for
OL,4,Ckilling teenager as he waited at bus
OL,5,Cstop
OL,7,F"Steven Wallace's actions on October
OL,8,F15, 2023, were utterly deplorable. He
OL,9,Fwas driving the vehicle in a hugely
OL,10,Freckless manner when he lost control
OL,11,Fand it ploughed into the bus stop at
OL,12,Fwhich Joe and the other people injured
OL,13,Fwere stood at.
OL,15,F"Not only that, Wallace then fled the
OL,16,Fscene instead of raising the alarm as
OL,17,Fhe should have done.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
